OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776438666
OL,3,CLebanon wakes to a welcome but fragile
OL,4,Cpeace, many wonder if it will last
OL,6,FThe Iranian-backed militia ` the most
OL,7,Fpowerful military force in this
OL,8,Fcountry ` is deeply embedded with the
OL,9,FShia community.
OL,11,FBut its critics here blame it for
OL,12,Fdragging Lebanon into a series of
OL,13,Fbloody and costly conflicts.
OL,15,FHezbollah has been weakened ` its
OL,16,Fsupply lines of arms and money from
OL,17,FIran badly disrupted ` but the
OL,18,FLebanese government is not strong
OL,19,Fenough to disarm it by force.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
